{"title":"In the Drops: Apidura visibility vest, Restrap hike-a-bike harness, Matchy Cycling kit, and Velocio trail jacket","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/apidura-visibility-vest","date":1693561913000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/apidura-visibility-vest\">In the Drops: Apidura visibility vest, Restrap hike-a-bike harness, Matchy Cycling kit, and Velocio trail jacket</a></p>\n\n<p>What do you call numbers which are always on the move? Roamin’ numerals. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It made me chuckle so I decided to share some humour on this funky Friday, which just so happens to be the first day of September. But not the first day of<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/vuelta-a-espana-route-race-reports-tv-guide-and-all-you-need-to-know\" target=\"_blank\"> the Vuelta</a>. The battle for the red jersey continues, as does the fight for kudos among the Cyclist team after pitching their race <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/vuelta-espana-predictions-2023\" target=\"_blank\">predictions</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Elsewhere, the Tour of Britain returns this Sunday so <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tour-of-britain-route-riders-live-tv-guide-all-you-need-to-know\" target=\"_blank\">here’s all you need to know</a> – knowing this lovely country it’s umbrellas at the ready.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the tech world, Shimano launched its <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/shimano-grx-mechanical-12-speed\" target=\"_blank\">GRX 12-speed mechanical groupset</a> and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/wilier-adlar-gravel-bike\" target=\"_blank\">Wilier its new gravel bike</a>, plus we already have a<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/shimano-grx-rx820-groupset-review\" target=\"_blank\"> review for that fancy new groupset</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Speaking of reviews, we’ve got them coming out of our ears: <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/garmin-edge-840-solar-review\" target=\"_blank\">Garmin’s Edge 840 Solar bike computer</a>, the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/shimano-105-pd-r7000-pedals-review\" target=\"_blank\">Shimano 105 PD-R7000 </a>and <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/wahoo-speedplay-comp-review\" target=\"_blank\">Wahoo Speedplay Comp</a> pedals, plus the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/maap-womens-team-bib-evo-shorts-review\" target=\"_blank\">Maap Team Evo bib shorts</a>. Spot the massive grin.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>We’ve also collated the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-single-speed-bikes\" target=\"_blank\">best single-speed bikes</a> for all the fixed-gear fanatics as well as the <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/buyers-guide-best-bikepacking-bags\" target=\"_blank\">best bikepacking bags</a> for the explorers among us. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have you heard of Dr Kawashima’s Brain Training? Me neither, but apparently it was a big thing. Luckily, we’ve gone one better with <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/cycling-mental-training\" target=\"_blank\">how to keep your mind in shape according to sports psychologists</a>. Move over Nintendo.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/shimano-grx-mechanical-12-speed\">New mechanical 12-speed Shimano GRX groupsets bring huge gear range to gravel  </a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/2023-pro-cycling-vuelta-espana-1\">Pro Log: Four arrested for planned protest at the Vuelta, Cecilie Uttrup Ludwig lights up Tour of Scandinavia as Annemiek van Vleuten wins overall, Marianne Vos ends season after surgery and Josh Tarling becomes joint youngest WorldTour stage winner</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/vuelta-a-espana-route-race-reports-tv-guide-and-all-you-need-to-know\">Vuelta a España 2023: Stage-by-stage preview and everything we know so far</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/tour-of-britain-route-riders-live-tv-guide-all-you-need-to-know\">Tour of Britain 2023: Route, start list and all you need to know</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>Apidura Packable Visibility Vest</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"cyclist wearing hi vis vest\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-10.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption>Emma Cole / Cyclist</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Why did the banana go to the doctor? It wasn’t peeling well.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I know, hilarious right? What’s not funny is feeling unseen on country lanes or wherever you ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Apidura packable visibility vest is certified to the European EN 17353 standard, so it’s compliant for use at events such as Paris-Brest-Paris, as well as other audax and ultra-distance competitions. A fair few riders were wearing it on the Transcontinental Race this summer, including the winner Christoph Strasser.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"cyclist wearing hi vis vest\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-11.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It features 360-degree graphics designed around on-bike position and night-time reflectivity, so you can shine bright like a diamond. The straps are adjustable, and it is easy to wear over bulky layers. Plus when you don’t need it, the vest scrunches down into next to nothing.  </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Apidura have seen some serious demand for this vest, and the brand expects availability in mid September.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://www.apidura.com/shop/packable-visibility-vest/\" target=\"_blank\">Apidura (£45)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Restrap Hike A Bike Harness</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"cyclist with bike harness on back\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-6.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Ever wanted to sling your bike onto your back and run up a hill? Well, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/restrap-bags-cycling\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap</a> has made the perfect harness to let you do just that.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its hike-a-bike harness is waterproof, handmade in the UK and comes with a lifetime warranty. And Restrap says it will fit any bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>At first glance it might seem a little complicated. Often things with tons of straps that say they are ‘quick and easy’ to fit really aren’t. But I am pleased to announce that the Restrap harness is genuinely quick and easy to attach and quite straightforward all together.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"cyclist with bike harness on back\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-7.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Once on, it is simply a case of wearing the bike like a backpack. When you’ve had enough of scrambling with a bike on your back, the harness wraps up neatly to sit on your bike and doesn’t interfere with riding.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This harness has got me inspired about many an adventure involving wheels and feet.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://restrap.com/products/hike-a-bike-harness\" target=\"_blank\">Restrap (£49.99)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Matchy Cycling kit</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"matchy cycling kit\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-19.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Founded in 2016, Matchy Cycling is a French brand based in Annecy – which is no joke – and produces some cracking kit. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Origins 2.0 jersey in leopard print is just such a vibe, and you can also get it in pink.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"matchy cycling kit comfort break feature\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-18.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>I really like the women’s Altitude shorts. They are seriously comfortable with a decent amount of compression and a neat comfort break feature. At €169 they are priced premium for a premium bit of kit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What I like more is that all of Matchy’s products are made from 30-100% recycled materials, and this year the brand began tracking its footprint and is working with third parties to help understand it. Matchy also hopes to become a B Corp by the end of this year.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Autumn never looked so good.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Check out the full range at <a href=\"https://www.matchycycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Matchy Cycling </a> </strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Velocio ultralight trail hooded jacket</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"velocio trail jacket\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-16.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/james-hayden-cyclist\" target=\"_blank\">Ultracyclist James Hayden</a>’s piece of advice to <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/mountains-of-heaven-silk-road-mountain-race\" target=\"_blank\">Silk Road Mountain Race</a> riders was to wear a hooded jacket and so, regardless of the fact I wasn’t taking on the race, I heeded his advice and went for the hooded jacket.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Velocio ultralight trail hooded jacket is made from windproof and water-resistant Pertex Quantum Air fabric, which is said to be very breathable and provides good protection from the elements. It also benefits from PFC and PFA Free DWR treatment, which means its waterproofing technology isn’t killing the environment.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"velocio trail jacket\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/08/emma-ITD-sept2023-14.jpg 2000w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The elastic hood fits over a helmet for when the rain starts pelting (UK summer I’m looking at you) and there’s a nice two-way zipper for adjustability.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The jacket feels great on, is a nice length and is super-comfy. It gives me the feeling of being one of those jackets you wear or bring along for many a cycling occasion.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I like it a lot.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Buy now from <a href=\"https://velocio.cc/collections/womens-off-road-jackets/products/womens-ultralight-trail-hooded-jacket\" target=\"_blank\">Velocio ($189)</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/apidura-visibility-vest\">In the Drops: Apidura visibility vest, Restrap hike-a-bike harness, Matchy Cycling kit, and Velocio trail jacket</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Emma Cole &#124; Features Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"febdfea1010cb23e918d0a0a50fcf3c367fc4bf54117797709407b2c4b5b3ccc","category":"Cycling"}